    <item>
      <title>Keystone 石油管道部分关闭，导致期货走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/keystone-oil-pipeline-segment-shuts-sending-futures-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TC Energy Corp 的 Keystone 石油管道周四部分关闭，该管道将加拿大重质原油输送到美国中西部和墨西哥湾沿岸，导致石油期货在结算后交易中走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/keystone-oil-pipeline-segment-shuts-sending-futures-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
